          <h2> Dr. Calvin Campbell : Comparison of large contourite... (27-02-2015) </h2> 
          <p>&nbsp;</p> 
          <p><img style="border: 0px none #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; vertical-align: middle;" src="/upload/images/babillard/seminaires/logo_seminaires_geotop4.jpg" alt="logo seminaires geotop" height="82" width="115"></p> 
          <h3>&nbsp;</h3> 
          <table style="width: 569px; height: 187px;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"> 
           <tbody> 
            <tr style="height: 20px;" valign="bottom"> 
             <td colspan="2"> <h3 style="text-align: center;">Dr. Calvin Campbell, Ressources naturelles Canada</h3> </td> 
            </tr> 
            <tr style="height: 20px;"> 
             <td colspan="2"> <h3 style="text-align: center;"><em>Comparison of large contourite drifts in the western North Atlantic</em></h3> </td> 
            </tr> 
            <tr style="height: 30px;" valign="bottom"> 
             <td colspan="2"> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: red;">Vendredi 27 février 2015 à 11h00 / Friday, February 27, 2015, 11:00am</span></strong></p> </td> 
            </tr> 
            <tr style="height: 10px;"> 
             <td colspan="2"> <p style="text-align: center;">Local PK-7605, 201 ave. Président-Kennedy, <span style="color: red;">UQAM</span></p> </td> 
            </tr> 
           </tbody> 
          </table> 
          <h4>Résumé / Abstract</h4> 
